About Me
I am Luchian, alternatively recognised as Steven, and I proudly identify as a graphic designer with a passion for both appreciating and crafting visual aesthetics. Interactive web design and 3D artistry holds a particular allure for me, occupying a significant place of my projects. Additionally, I find joy in practicing photography as a complementary endeavour.

This digital portfolio is still under work.
